django-gstorage
===============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/django-gstorage.svg
   :alt: PyPi page
   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-gstorage

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/fyndiq/django-gstorage.svg?branch=master
